Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the SC. I want to just\Nuh make sure I mention all these for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,people who haven't been to these\Nlectures before. Those who have been
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,here before or have truth versus false\Nalready. I put it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is always true.\NThat which emanates from the self with a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,capital S or by divine incarnation\Nuh is always the same. It comes on as an
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,inner radiance knowingness. It's silent,\Nnonverbal, is exquisite. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,transformative\Nand it's always the same. Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the great sages of ancient India of\Nancient India
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,uh five or six\Nthousand years BC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the great Aryan sages out of which came\Nthe Hindu religions and viata etc. uh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever their experience of the truth\Nis the same as it is in in the present
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,day.\NTruth is does not exclude anybody. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:02:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nonsecreative. It's nonsecular.\NIt's non sectarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have any secrets.\NDoes the sky have any secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the sun radiating forth have any\Nsecrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for $250. I will whisper in your ear.\NI see you've been there, huh? I think it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was $250\Nfrom John Trumpet. Okay, that's $ 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it for a second with it. $250\Nsecret. What's the purpose of secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of secret is to control,\Nisn't it? Why would you want to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,anything secret, right?\NIf it takes you to love, what love wants
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to share.\NYou want to share with people. You can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,rationalize charging by saying if they\Nget it for free, they won't value it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a clever rationalization of\Npeople who charge money so they don't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,feel guilty about it.\NYou could have some other requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,not necessarily monetary,\Nbut you would see the quick loss of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,interest in many of these organizations\Nif the requirement was not a monetary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,one.\NAvailable should be open, available,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,written, verbal,\Nvideos, audios, lectures, books,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever. Integrity of the purpose.\NThere's nothing to gain or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If nobody listens to the lecture, that's\Nfine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody listens to the lecture, that's\Nfine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:04:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's nobody here, I wouldn't have\Nto make the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? So, why is this? It's because\Nthrough any of these meditative or
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplative styles, eventually you\Nbecome the field. The field that is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,complete and total in itself. It has\Nnothing to gain. It's not lacking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. It just is.\NThat which is has no needs or nothing to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,gain. The fact that three people come to\Nyour lecture or 30,000 is all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same. It's all the same.\NWhy? Because your obligation is to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself and to God. The reason we're\Ngoing to talk about 8:50 this afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is I don't want to go back on the other\Nside and you didn't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the obligation to divinity and\Nseeing divinity as expressed as the life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as human life. So out of your love for\Nlife and your obligation and your love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for God, you you want to share all that\Nyou you know for the benefit of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,\Nif you got to the top of a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,mountain, it's your obligation to share\Nwith the new climbers what to expect up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Sometimes, I can't believe it.\NHere's a group that goes up there with a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,guide. This guy, I'd sue the pants off\Nhim. Takes them up to 12 or 14,000 ft
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with no oxygen.\NAnd and an experienced guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god. So if you're going to make a\Nlong climb, a teacher should tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what it's like, what the north slope is\Nlike, what hours you can do that. And
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to get much strength\Nunless you get a supplementary oxygen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,over 12,000 14,000 ft. So these people\Nbarely survive. And you know, the death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,rate of people trying to get to the top\Nof Everest is extremely high. I forget
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,how many die every year. 19 or 20 or\Nsomething. Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,>> yeah. So therefore, a guide should tell\Nyou what to look out for along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when your father taught you\Nhow to drive or your mother as as it may
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,be in today's world. Uh my father taught\Nme never trust the other driver. Always
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,presume he's drunk and stupid.\NJust because his left turn indicator is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,going doesn't mean he's going to turn\Nleft. He could just as well turn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He got confused left and right. So\Nhappily I never had a serious accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was a cab driver for many years\Nand I've driven like a million miles. So
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all right. So we we have an obligation.\NI'm the gain and lose. Uh truth is not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the expos it's not sectarian independent\Nof opinion. Uh we're not interested to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,say what people's opinion is. Has no\Npositions on anything. Truth is not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,anti- anything. Why? Because falsehood\Nis not the opposite of truth. It's the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,absence.\NNo requirements or demands. You don't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,have to take any oaths, sign up for\Nanything. No required memberships. You
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to swear on on top of\Nsomething. Uh non-controlling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher has no interest in the\Npersonal lives of individuals unless
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they bring them up for discussion within\Na spiritual context. I mean, of what
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,interest would it be to a spiritual\Nteacher? what your sex life is, what how
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you cut cut your hair, what you wear.\NYou know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should a spiritual teacher is\Ntalking about a whole different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,dimension have any interest in your\Npersonal life? I mean, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a person could say, "Look, I\Nhave a compulsive sexuality and I'm just
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,driving me nuts." That's a different\Nthing. See, but I'm not telling him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,look, don't have sex with about 30, 40\Npeople in a row like that. uh it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,my place to be telling him. I'll tell\Nyou why. Another reason because I rob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,him of the karmic merit. Do you\Nunderstand? If I do a thing through
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,threat, intimidation, and and by\Nswinging my weight around, I've just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,deprived him of the karmic benefit of\Nhaving seen that for himself and chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend that. You know, when he\Nsays, "I don't want to be run by list
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore. It's driving me crazy." And I\Nsay, 'Well, if you want to be a member
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of our group here, uh, you can't have\Nsex there. Now, he's conforming out of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of my authority, but he's he's\Ngained no karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,>> He's doing it out of fear of my\Nopinion of him, etc. See, so I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,like, you know, there's no point to\Ncontrol people because you deprive them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of karmic merit.\NTherefore, hitting bottom is a necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,step for many people and we all have hit\Nbottom or none of us would be in this
