Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of times or you know seemingly\Nminor issue but we anguished over them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and made a change of direction. So a\Nchange of direction. So non-controlling
