Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they want to have group sex or what? I'm\Nnot going to tell them don't have group
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,sex. I mean, it's their problem\Nif you got the time for group sex. I
