Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,intimidation.\NI mean, if you don't come to these
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,lectures, we're not going to put a\Nrattlesnake in your mailbox. You know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,what I mean?\NWe don't want to brainwash anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want people going into\Nagilation of leaders, the great ba haha,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,bong bong, you know, and who needs all\Nthat theatrical ritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to brainwash people with\Nindoctrinations
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or intrusions into their private life.\NSo, we'll go into the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh we have to hurry through to be\Nthrough. We're not going to bind anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with any contracts, pledges, etc. And uh\Nthere's reasons for that. Uh it may seem
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,reasonable to you in this lifetime, but\Nyou know when you take a vow and swear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,by a follower or something like that,\Nyou know that you're responsible for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that for many many lifetimes,\N20 lifetimes from now. You don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what what's happening in your life. You\Nare held by the bond you just made. So
