Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NTherefore truth doesn't want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. It allows freedom, not\Nnon-binding
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,commonality.\NWho people are within the spiritual
